---
title: Mediterranean Tender Beef & Fusilli Stew with Pre-Cut Veggies & Parsley
description: We love a slow cooker dish - just throw in your ingredients, and come back later to a meal that is sure to be warm, hearty and comforting. This one involves a rich beef ragu with fusilli to keep you satisfied. We can’t wait to dig in!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

*We’ve replaced the risoni in this recipe with fusilli due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
